  "2404360": {
    "name": "翎之歌",
    "steam_appid": 2404360,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>QQ群：</strong>183930450</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>微博：</strong>YuKi游戏制作组</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404360/extras/19ea551bb5ab55eb9ec4dba491b16183.avif?t=1758455996\" width=234 height=224 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏介绍</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >作为这世界上最后的一个人类，你在沉睡数个纪元以后在人类消亡后的世界苏醒，与一群不知自己身份来历的幸存者一同在这地狱光景般的末日中夹缝求生，而你的苏醒似乎意味着新纪元的开始，整个世界的齿轮因你转动起来——作为人类文明改写历史最后的后手，你的到来会改变什么吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >人物介绍</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404360/extras/1cbf71d579a558e76e497244f5fb69bf.avif?t=1758455996\" width=206 height=180 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>杨帆（CV：白渡）</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家所扮演的角色，在埋葬着最后人类的墓园中被挖出来的人类，天生自带强大的钝感力，是短兵相接的战术天才。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404360/extras/369adf0ee977ee43b7c6c9f5c8d9556d.avif?t=1758455996\" width=206 height=180 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>翎小雨（CV：赵灵泽）</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >天生的怪物，运动神经与抗击打能力远超常人；有着绝对碾压其他人的战斗力，是神经病营地里最大的神经病</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404360/extras/c6018b4f268777ce64c7061ff13b771d.avif?t=1758455996\" width=206 height=180 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>染红霞（CV：赵灵泽）</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >和杨帆差不多同一时期进入营地的幸存者，有严重的洁癖，格外讨厌翎小雨。但同样又有着人类最为复杂的情感。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404360/extras/d8d80c71dd0faf87b6ac2ea5d92cabb2.avif?t=1758455996\" width=200 height=175 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>春泥儿（CV：予薇）</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >像坏人又像好人的少女，格外崇拜翎小雨，对翎小雨有着肉体及以上的非分之想。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404360/extras/7b4d872410c2f94636d204dbae4d2d49.avif?t=1758455996\" width=200 height=175 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>北微笑（CV：家康）</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >神经病营地的大脑，但他维持着营地的和平似乎别有用心，经过调查发现他的所有行为逻辑全部是围绕着一位女性展开的。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404360/extras/5a8556cb8be369ca39a46c065ae4391b.avif?t=1758455996\" width=206 height=180 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>龙三（CV：阳光煤气罐）</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >冷漠的少年，有着极强的动手能力的技术型人才，即便是在匮乏物资的时期，也依然用技术换得在营地的地位。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404360/extras/bce73eac4a9c31bfe25b9edfadf8b393.avif?t=1758455996\" width=206 height=180 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>邱雅琴（CV：闲踏梧桐）</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >纯真善良的少女。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404360/extras/ce0b904ba33f171f81597d7e6d8378e4.avif?t=1758455996\" width=206 height=180 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>林娜（CV：刘知否）</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >刀子嘴豆腐心的女人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404360/extras/1d1b459b089f683dfc5e5d0f336473fb.avif?t=1758455996\" width=206 height=181 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>殷草（CV：狐言）</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >储备粮。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404360/extras/9d7afc84c1d0c1221cacb1402cede0b7.avif?t=1758455996\" width=200 height=175 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>图生财（CV：三儿）</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >憨厚的大叔。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >剧情体验</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Yuki游戏制作组匠心打造的末日系文字冒险游戏第二作，倾情打造。总文本量60W+，有20个以上不同结局，玩家将在人类消亡的末日中扮演最后的人类——杨帆，并根据行进过程中的各类信息做出选择，不同的选择所导向的结局差异极大，本作延续了前作的黑暗风格与精彩剧情的同时，修正了游戏内繁杂的选项系统，并力求在人物刻画上做得更好。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >玩法设计</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>AVG系统</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  将人物立绘，背景、CG、文字、语音、BGM、音效等内容相结合的方式来演出剧情。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Flag系统</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  玩家的选择行动会获得不同的flag，这些flag在后续回收时会触发不同的剧情与结局。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>追逐战系统</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  文字追逐战，时间结束，将会迎来死亡结局。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>QTE系统</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  需要玩家在限定时间内对屏幕上的内容快速做出反应。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>好感度系统</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  好感度系统内可以看到不同好感下的人物，对主人公有不同的反馈，也会有新的剧情出现。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >视觉效果</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我们在视觉效果方面力求做到国产单机游戏的较高的水准；独树一帜的末日二次元风格主题，废墟与蓝色调的冰冷背景，让画面更显末日氛围与美感的兼顾。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >制作成员</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >制作团队：YuKi游戏制作组/崩溃猛犸</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >制作人：未来猫、咬定青山</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >监督：辟邪</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >剧情策划：未来猫</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >美术策划：咬定青山</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >配音导演：w小璃</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >分镜：<strong>鵺心</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >动画：江筱落</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >程序：伽蓝</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >演出：辟邪、伽蓝、未来猫、星空</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >校对/配置/演出协助：辟邪、星空、Chr_</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >音频后期：w小璃</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >美术协助：呱呱</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >UI/美宣：咬定青山</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >配乐：急冻秋刀鱼</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p>",
